    "metadata": {
        "sysdescription": "Athorn is an Al\u2019marey-pocket society built around modular living\u2014habitats, factories, even governance are snapped together like standardized blocks. That mindset makes Athorn excellent at producing consistent industrial goods and reliable warp subassemblies in small runs, ideal for fleets that can\u2019t afford long downtime. Visitors find Athorn\u2019s \u201cpolite distance\u201d unsettling: they\u2019re cooperative, but everything\u2014access, labour, even hospitality\u2014has a published spec and a price.",
